; *                                                   control block type.
; *                        OS_ERR_PNAME_NULL          You passed a NULL pointer for 'pname'
; *                        OS_ERR_PEVENT_NULL         if you passed a NULL pointer for 'pevent'
; *                        OS_ERR_NAME_SET_ISR        if you called this function from an ISR
