; *                                        (i.e. >= OS_LOWEST_PRIO) or, you have not specified OS_PRIO_SELF.
; *              OS_ERR_TASK_SUSPEND_PRIO  if the task to suspend does not exist
; *              OS_ERR_TASK_NOT_EXITS     if the task is assigned to a Mutex PIP
